<n>The</n> year is 2046. <n>Detective</n> <p>Ross Sylibus</p> is transferred to <n>Mars</n> when a country <n>singer</n> on her flight is murdered. <n>Making</n> matters more complicated is that the singer is a "<n>Third</n>"—a robot that looks and feels like a human. <p>Sylibus</p> is partnered with <p>Armitage</p>—a beautiful female cop with a bad attitude. <n>As</n> they <n>investigate</n> the murder of the singer and <n>other</n> women on Mars, they uncover a conspiracy that can have them both killed by the <n>Martian</n> government.

(Source: ANN) 
